WEBVTT

00:00:05.811 --> 00:00:08.216
Screaming Banshee Attack! Ha!

00:00:08.250 --> 00:00:10.889
[NARRATOR] Previously,
on Dragon Ball Z Kai,

00:00:10.922 --> 00:00:13.861
Gotenks displayed
overwhelming power

00:00:13.894 --> 00:00:17.603
after leveling up
to Super Saiyan 3.

00:00:17.636 --> 00:00:19.540
It seemed the universe
had finally found

00:00:19.573 --> 00:00:22.478
an answer for
the nightmare of Majin Buu.

00:00:22.512 --> 00:00:27.254
But Fusion has a limit, and the
boys had wasted precious time.

00:00:27.287 --> 00:00:30.762
A sharp turn for the worse. Now!

00:00:30.795 --> 00:00:32.732
Huh? Already?!

00:00:33.233 --> 00:00:38.409
♪ Opening Song ♪

00:02:08.858 --> 00:02:11.395
Uh oh.

00:02:14.936 --> 00:02:18.911
[PICCOLO gasps]

00:02:31.770 --> 00:02:35.343
This isn't good! He's gone
back to his basic level!

00:02:46.265 --> 00:02:53.413
[SUPER BUU groans]

00:02:57.021 --> 00:02:59.224
[SUPER BUU]
Aaah!

00:03:02.130 --> 00:03:05.905
--Boy.
--[GOTENKS] Eeh!

00:03:05.939 --> 00:03:06.941
[SUPER BUU chuckles]

00:03:06.974 --> 00:03:10.714
[GOTENKS chuckles nervously]

00:03:14.789 --> 00:03:16.225
[laughs nervously]

00:03:16.259 --> 00:03:18.597
Aah-ha-ha-ha! Yeah!

00:03:18.630 --> 00:03:21.870
Just as I planned! You betcha!

00:03:21.904 --> 00:03:23.473
[PICCOLO]
No. It's hopeless.

00:03:23.507 --> 00:03:27.448
This was our only chance left.
Damn it, Gotenks!

00:03:27.481 --> 00:03:30.554
Hey Elder Kai, we can't
wait! The boys have lost!

00:03:30.588 --> 00:03:33.393
Their Fusion's about to end!
We've got to act now!

00:03:33.427 --> 00:03:35.397
Dad, are you sure
they can't hold on?

00:03:35.430 --> 00:03:38.203
Yeah. They'll get killed
like this.

00:03:38.236 --> 00:03:40.574
[ELDER KAI]
Okay, you can run along now.

00:03:40.608 --> 00:03:43.012
Actually, we finished up
a while ago.

00:03:43.046 --> 00:03:44.883
--[GOHAN] Huh?
--[GOKU] Wha--?

00:03:44.916 --> 00:03:46.286
[ALL]
A while ago?

00:03:46.319 --> 00:03:47.589
What do you mean?

00:03:47.622 --> 00:03:49.158
How long have I been
sitting here for nothing?

00:03:49.191 --> 00:03:52.164
Mmm... Oh, I don't know.
Five minutes maybe?

00:03:52.197 --> 00:03:53.835
Then why didn't you
tell me that sooner?

00:03:53.868 --> 00:03:55.404
I could be fighting already!

00:03:55.437 --> 00:03:57.040
I thought you said
I wasn't finished yet

00:03:57.074 --> 00:03:58.577
because I wasn't focusing!

00:03:58.611 --> 00:04:01.951
You dope! I was just stalling
to make things more dramatic.

00:04:01.984 --> 00:04:03.353
Don't you know anything?

00:04:03.386 --> 00:04:05.123
[ALL]
Uuh!

00:04:06.092 --> 00:04:10.166
The boys are in trouble!
I've got to get moving and fast!

00:04:10.200 --> 00:04:12.237
You've unlocked all this
hidden energy, right?

00:04:12.271 --> 00:04:14.509
So what now?
How do I tap into it?

00:04:14.542 --> 00:04:17.348
Well, you know how you guys
are always screaming

00:04:17.381 --> 00:04:19.452
and turning
Super-whatever-you-call-it?

00:04:19.485 --> 00:04:21.255
Yeah, kinda like that.

00:04:21.289 --> 00:04:23.292
You just need
to show some spunk.

00:04:23.326 --> 00:04:25.832
So it's basically like
going Super Saiyan, huh?

00:04:25.865 --> 00:04:26.667
Okay, let's see.

00:04:26.700 --> 00:04:28.904
Hold on, wait 'til I step back!

00:04:28.937 --> 00:04:37.187
[GOHAN yells]

00:04:37.221 --> 00:04:38.289
[ELDER KAI hollers]

00:04:38.322 --> 00:04:40.561
[GOKU shrieks]

00:04:42.532 --> 00:04:44.235
[ELDER KAI hollers]

00:04:44.268 --> 00:04:46.607
[GOKU gasps]

00:04:46.640 --> 00:04:49.779
--[SUPREME KAI hollers]
--[KIBITO groans]

00:05:26.987 --> 00:05:28.657
[ELDER KAI] Little brat!
He could have at least

00:05:28.690 --> 00:05:31.663
let me get out
of his blast zone.

00:05:36.907 --> 00:05:39.111
Wow. It's true.

00:05:41.215 --> 00:05:43.554
This is awesome, Dad.
I feel great!

00:05:43.587 --> 00:05:46.125
[GOKU] You don't have to tell
me; I'm standing right here.

00:05:46.158 --> 00:05:48.630
It's like you're
bursting at the seams!

00:05:49.766 --> 00:05:53.072
Remarkable. He's gone
far beyond the normal limits

00:05:53.105 --> 00:05:54.208
of his power.

00:05:54.241 --> 00:05:56.947
It sure is hard
to believe. Look at him.

00:05:56.981 --> 00:06:00.253
On the outside, it doesn't seem
like much has changed at all.

00:06:00.286 --> 00:06:02.324
I mean, he's not even
Super Saiyan,

00:06:02.357 --> 00:06:05.163
but his strength
is way off the charts.

00:06:05.196 --> 00:06:08.671
Heh. You put too much
stock in your transformations.

00:06:08.704 --> 00:06:11.342
That Super-whatever trick
is overrated.

00:06:11.375 --> 00:06:13.280
Gohan, we need
to get you back to Earth.

00:06:13.313 --> 00:06:14.549
If we don't act quickly,

00:06:14.583 --> 00:06:16.620
we could lose our chance
to stop that monster.

00:06:16.654 --> 00:06:19.158
Kibito and I will take you.
Let's finish this mess.

00:06:19.192 --> 00:06:23.299
I'm sorry. I believe it's best
I take him there on my own, sir.

00:06:23.333 --> 00:06:24.468
Uh!

00:06:24.503 --> 00:06:25.905
What are you saying?
That's my choice!

00:06:25.938 --> 00:06:28.110
It's my responsibility
as Supreme Kai

00:06:28.143 --> 00:06:29.378
to see this to the end.

00:06:29.412 --> 00:06:31.416
Forgive me, but you'll
only be a liability--

00:06:31.449 --> 00:06:33.587
someone Buu could use
against Gohan.

00:06:33.620 --> 00:06:35.090
I don't plan to stay, either.

00:06:35.123 --> 00:06:39.097
I'll return as soon as I've
taken him to the battlefield.

00:06:39.131 --> 00:06:42.471
A warrior this great won't need
any distractions from us.

00:06:42.505 --> 00:06:44.575
Thanks, Kibito.

00:06:45.410 --> 00:06:47.715
Yes, you're right.
The only thing I would do

00:06:47.748 --> 00:06:51.322
is slow him down.
Just be careful.

00:06:51.355 --> 00:06:52.825
I'm sorry, Gohan.

00:06:52.859 --> 00:06:55.463
But my place is here
in Otherworld now.

00:06:55.497 --> 00:06:57.602
I won't be going
with you this time.

00:06:57.635 --> 00:06:59.806
I wish I could've
been there, you know.

00:06:59.839 --> 00:07:02.879
To watch you grow
into the man you've become.

00:07:02.912 --> 00:07:04.081
I know, Dad.

00:07:04.115 --> 00:07:06.820
I guess this is the
last time I'll get to see you.

00:07:06.853 --> 00:07:10.561
Or at least until you join me
here one day. Heh.

00:07:10.594 --> 00:07:13.701
Good luck, son. Give Buu
exactly what he deserves.

00:07:13.734 --> 00:07:15.638
I will.

00:07:22.619 --> 00:07:25.524
All right. Off you go, son.

00:07:27.596 --> 00:07:30.601
Until we meet again, Dad.

00:07:36.079 --> 00:07:39.520
[ELDER KAI] Ungrateful boy.
He didn't even thank me.

00:07:39.553 --> 00:07:42.124
When I'm the one
who worked all the magic!

00:07:42.157 --> 00:07:43.994
These kids today.

00:07:53.847 --> 00:07:57.454
And here we are.
It's up to you, Gohan.

00:07:57.488 --> 00:07:58.724
-[GOHAN] Wait.
-[KIBITO] Hm?

00:07:58.757 --> 00:08:01.028
Before you go,
can I ask you a favor?

00:08:01.061 --> 00:08:03.099
I need something special
for this fight.

00:08:03.132 --> 00:08:05.904
I want to dress like
my father does to honor him.

00:08:05.938 --> 00:08:08.844
Can you make me an orange
fighting <i>gi</i> just like his?

00:08:08.878 --> 00:08:12.986
[KIBITO] Mm. Of course.
Should be simple enough.

00:08:13.019 --> 00:08:15.490
Let's see. I believe
the color was the same

00:08:15.525 --> 00:08:18.062
as the frog dung
on Planet Popol.

00:08:18.095 --> 00:08:21.503
Okay. Guess I'll
take your word on that.

00:08:26.446 --> 00:08:29.351
Yeah, that's perfect.
Thanks, it means a lot.

00:08:29.384 --> 00:08:31.255
You're welcome.
It's a fitting tribute.

00:08:31.289 --> 00:08:34.028
Now it's time I go,
but I wish you a great victory,

00:08:34.061 --> 00:08:36.432
and the World of the Kais
will be cheering for you.

00:08:36.465 --> 00:08:41.041
Bye, Kibito. And give my regards
to both Supreme Kais, okay?

00:08:54.335 --> 00:08:56.806
All right. Here we go.

00:09:04.589 --> 00:09:06.392
[PICCOLO]
How could they run out of time?

00:09:06.425 --> 00:09:07.762
Darn those kids!

00:09:07.796 --> 00:09:10.667
Why do they have to go
and drag out their battle?!

00:09:17.682 --> 00:09:19.318
[GOTENKS]
Eeeh!

00:09:19.351 --> 00:09:21.355
[SUPER BUU growls]

00:09:21.388 --> 00:09:23.460
[GOTENKS hollers]

00:09:23.493 --> 00:09:25.130
[GOTENKS] I'm running low
on options here.

00:09:25.163 --> 00:09:28.770
But if I have to bluff
my way out, then so be it.

00:09:28.804 --> 00:09:31.876
[SUPER BUU chuckles]

00:09:31.910 --> 00:09:33.045
Hm?

00:09:33.078 --> 00:09:39.725
Super Ghost Kamikaze--hm!
Attack!

00:09:44.101 --> 00:09:45.103
[SUPER BUU grunts]

00:09:45.136 --> 00:09:49.612
[GHOSTS laughing]

00:09:50.479 --> 00:09:52.250
[GOTENKS laughs]

00:09:52.284 --> 00:09:54.689
It may look like I've
gone back to the way I was,

00:09:54.723 --> 00:09:57.227
but my power's
actually increased!

00:09:57.261 --> 00:09:59.198
Go! Get him, Ghosts!

00:09:59.231 --> 00:10:02.671
Time to show our
super extra awesome power!

00:10:02.705 --> 00:10:04.909
[GHOSTS]
Huuuuh?!

00:10:06.011 --> 00:10:07.782
[GHOST 1]
Super extra awesome what?

00:10:07.815 --> 00:10:09.819
[GHOST 4] Yeah, I don't know;
he looks pretty strong.

00:10:09.853 --> 00:10:11.489
[GHOST 6]
We just got here!

00:10:11.523 --> 00:10:13.259
Quit your whining
and do what you're told!

00:10:13.292 --> 00:10:14.629
Go now!

00:10:14.662 --> 00:10:16.633
[GHOSTS laugh]

00:10:16.667 --> 00:10:18.369
[SUPER BUU]
Heh.

00:10:19.539 --> 00:10:21.075
[GHOSTS]
Uh?

00:10:21.610 --> 00:10:25.984
--[SUPER BUU yells]
--[GHOSTS yelling]

00:10:31.529 --> 00:10:34.334
Perfect. Now's my chance to run!

00:10:39.478 --> 00:10:43.118
[GOTENKS groaning]

00:10:48.129 --> 00:10:49.999
[hollers]

00:10:51.135 --> 00:10:52.805
[SUPER BUU laughs]

00:10:54.207 --> 00:10:55.711
[GOTENKS groans]

00:10:55.745 --> 00:10:59.150
[yelling]

00:11:03.594 --> 00:11:08.604
[BOTH] Damn you!
This is bad! We're split!

00:11:08.637 --> 00:11:11.174
The Fusion must've worn off!

00:11:15.116 --> 00:11:19.725
[BOTH gasping]

00:11:51.455 --> 00:11:52.926
[TRUNKS]
Oh, we're in trouble.

00:11:52.959 --> 00:11:55.196
Can't believe
we ran out of Fusion time!

00:11:55.230 --> 00:11:58.804
[GOTEN] What do we do?
He could maybe kill us now.

00:11:58.837 --> 00:12:00.575
No "maybe" about it!
You know what he did

00:12:00.608 --> 00:12:02.778
to everyone else.
We're goners for sure!

00:12:02.812 --> 00:12:04.882
Yeah. You're right.

00:12:06.586 --> 00:12:10.126
Aah! Hey,
what if we run for it?

00:12:10.159 --> 00:12:13.265
You really think
he'd let that happen?

00:12:14.669 --> 00:12:19.044
[SUPER BUU breathes deeply]

00:12:19.077 --> 00:12:21.749
Ooh, I guess not.
We're done for.

00:12:21.783 --> 00:12:23.987
How can this
be happening? No fair!

00:12:24.020 --> 00:12:25.991
We're just kids;
we can't die yet!

00:12:26.025 --> 00:12:29.298
Yeah. I'm not ready
to be a ghost.

00:12:29.331 --> 00:12:32.136
--[SUPER BUU growls]
--[GOTEN, TRUNKS gasp]

00:12:35.944 --> 00:12:37.981
--[TRUNKS] Piccolo?
--I doubt I'll be much help,

00:12:38.015 --> 00:12:40.287
but I won't let you
face this alone.

00:12:40.320 --> 00:12:43.492
We'll give him our best.
And die together.

00:12:43.526 --> 00:12:46.164
[TRUNKS] Our best?
We won't be close to our best!

00:12:46.198 --> 00:12:48.503
We couldn't finish him
when we were fused, Piccolo!

00:12:48.537 --> 00:12:51.008
And without it, we don't
stand a chance against him!

00:12:51.042 --> 00:12:52.344
[GOTEN]
Yeah, Trunks is right!

00:12:52.377 --> 00:12:54.247
Maybe it doesn't matter
to you 'cause you're old,

00:12:54.281 --> 00:12:56.753
but we're not! We don't
want to die like this!

00:12:56.786 --> 00:12:57.922
This is crazy!

00:12:57.955 --> 00:12:59.224
[TRUNKS]
Super crazy!

00:12:59.258 --> 00:13:01.629
I'm scared, Trunks.
What should we do?

00:13:01.663 --> 00:13:03.500
I got it.

00:13:03.534 --> 00:13:05.336
Our extra-last resort.

00:13:05.369 --> 00:13:06.807
Oh yeah, I forgot!

00:13:06.840 --> 00:13:08.309
[PICCOLO]
Hm?

00:13:08.342 --> 00:13:10.446
[TRUNKS] Let's tell
Majin Buu we're sorry.

00:13:10.480 --> 00:13:12.116
[PICCOLO]
Aaaugh!

00:13:12.150 --> 00:13:14.455
Yeah. He's not the
sharpest tool in the shed

00:13:14.488 --> 00:13:16.392
so we can prob'ly
trick him into forgiving us

00:13:16.425 --> 00:13:18.697
if we just act really sorry
and give him candy

00:13:18.730 --> 00:13:19.933
and tell him how great he is!

00:13:19.966 --> 00:13:22.070
Mhmm! We can use
our cute little kid act.

00:13:22.104 --> 00:13:23.807
Grown ups always
fall for that trick!

00:13:23.840 --> 00:13:25.878
Then, we can buy
enough time to fuse again

00:13:25.911 --> 00:13:27.615
and defeat him for real!

00:13:27.648 --> 00:13:30.052
You gotta be kidding.

00:13:30.086 --> 00:13:32.190
Yeah! It's a perfect plan!

00:13:32.224 --> 00:13:34.829
You find the candy,
I'll do the rest!

00:13:34.863 --> 00:13:38.102
[laughs]
Uh, ooh.

00:13:38.903 --> 00:13:41.075
[TRUNKS]
Hm?

00:13:41.108 --> 00:13:44.181
Wait. I don't think there are
any candy stores nearby.

00:13:44.214 --> 00:13:46.151
Hmmm. Yeah,
that's a good point.

00:13:46.185 --> 00:13:47.420
We could search the world

00:13:47.454 --> 00:13:49.058
but Buu's prob'ly
destroyed 'em all by now.

00:13:49.091 --> 00:13:52.096
And there aren't any
candy makers left, either.

00:13:52.130 --> 00:13:53.934
[TRUNKS] This plan
definitely has some holes.

00:13:53.967 --> 00:13:55.202
[GOTEN]
Hm.

00:13:55.236 --> 00:13:58.275
[grunts] Enough!
You're just talking nonsense!

00:13:58.309 --> 00:14:05.256
[yawning]

00:14:06.325 --> 00:14:07.761
What?

00:14:07.795 --> 00:14:09.364
[GOTEN]
What happened to him?

00:14:09.398 --> 00:14:11.068
[TRUNKS]
Beats me.

00:14:14.140 --> 00:14:16.579
Uh! Listen, do you hear that?

00:14:16.613 --> 00:14:18.616
[SUPER BUU snoring]

00:14:28.102 --> 00:14:32.511
O-Okay. That's weird.
But I think he's... snoring.

00:14:32.544 --> 00:14:35.684
Yeah, you're right.
It does sound like snoring.

00:14:35.717 --> 00:14:37.087
He's loud, too.

00:14:37.120 --> 00:14:39.592
[PICCOLO] I don't understand.
Is he toying with us?

00:14:39.626 --> 00:14:41.194
Or could he actually be--?

00:14:41.228 --> 00:14:42.832
Augh! Hey!

00:14:42.865 --> 00:14:44.502
We're just gonna
check on him. We'll be back!

00:14:44.536 --> 00:14:48.075
No, don't get close!
We need to use this opportunity!

00:14:48.109 --> 00:14:58.328
[SUPER BUU snoring]

00:15:06.880 --> 00:15:10.386
[SUPER BUU snoring]

00:15:10.419 --> 00:15:12.390
[BOTH shriek]

00:15:13.626 --> 00:15:19.638
[SUPER BUU continues snoring]

00:15:26.452 --> 00:15:29.157
[GOTEN]
Uh, hello?

00:15:30.159 --> 00:15:33.600
No reaction at all. He really
did fall asleep, didn't he?

00:15:33.634 --> 00:15:36.205
I'm not so sure. Maybe he's
just trying to trick us.

00:15:36.238 --> 00:15:37.575
That's something we would do.

00:15:37.608 --> 00:15:39.612
Yeah, good point. Let's see.

00:15:39.645 --> 00:15:42.117
Maybe if we pull really hard
on that thing on his head,

00:15:42.150 --> 00:15:43.820
it'll scare him
and he'll open his eyes

00:15:43.853 --> 00:15:46.424
so we know
he's pretending. I'll try.

00:15:49.164 --> 00:15:54.742
[GOTEN] Upsy-daisy.
Just a little bit more.

00:15:54.775 --> 00:15:56.913
Stop that!
What's wrong with you?

00:15:56.947 --> 00:15:58.851
Are you completely insane?

00:15:58.884 --> 00:16:00.086
[TRUNKS, GOTEN]
Huh?

00:16:00.119 --> 00:16:01.155
He was moments away
from destroying you both

00:16:01.188 --> 00:16:02.457
and now that he's fallen asleep

00:16:02.490 --> 00:16:05.429
you want to go and
wake him up on purpose? Ah!

00:16:05.462 --> 00:16:07.099
[PICCOLO quietly]
I don't know why he's sleeping

00:16:07.133 --> 00:16:09.371
or what he's planning, but I
honestly don't care either!

00:16:09.404 --> 00:16:11.175
We just need to take
every minute he gives us,

00:16:11.208 --> 00:16:13.980
so you boys can rest
and get ready to fuse again!

00:16:14.013 --> 00:16:16.185
It's our only play. Now come on!

00:16:16.218 --> 00:16:18.021
[TRUNKS, GOTEN]
'Kay.

00:16:19.024 --> 00:16:20.594
[PICCOLO exhales]

00:16:21.863 --> 00:16:22.998
What?

00:16:23.032 --> 00:16:24.769
[SUPER BUU]
Huh?

00:16:24.802 --> 00:16:26.438
[PICCOLO]
What is that energy?

00:16:26.471 --> 00:16:27.942
Somebody's coming!

00:16:28.644 --> 00:16:31.381
[PICCOLO] But who could it be?
There's no one left!

00:16:31.415 --> 00:16:34.321
And that power's
unbelievably strong!

00:16:34.354 --> 00:16:38.095
Could this be
some new foe? Or an ally?

00:16:39.899 --> 00:16:41.736
[growls]

00:16:44.140 --> 00:16:46.144
[PICCOLO]
It's Goku!

00:16:50.654 --> 00:16:54.094
No, it's not my dad;
it's my brother! He's okay!

00:16:54.127 --> 00:16:55.764
Gohan's alive?

00:16:57.768 --> 00:17:00.039
That can't be!

00:17:08.022 --> 00:17:10.627
[SUPER BUU growls]

00:17:18.944 --> 00:17:20.914
I'm glad I wasn't too late.

00:17:20.947 --> 00:17:22.050
Wow, it is you!

00:17:22.083 --> 00:17:23.753
I'm so glad to see you're okay!

00:17:23.786 --> 00:17:25.490
Then you never did die,
did you?!

00:17:25.524 --> 00:17:28.295
No, it was a close call,
but then Supreme Kai saved me

00:17:28.328 --> 00:17:29.899
and took me back to his world.

00:17:29.933 --> 00:17:33.707
I've been there the whole time
getting ready for this showdown.

00:17:33.740 --> 00:17:35.944
[growls]

00:17:35.977 --> 00:17:37.347
[PICCOLO]
That's Gohan, all right,

00:17:37.380 --> 00:17:39.450
but something's
changed about him.

00:17:39.484 --> 00:17:41.322
He's carrying
himself differently,

00:17:41.355 --> 00:17:43.594
and there's a whole new
look in his eyes.

00:17:43.627 --> 00:17:44.962
But it's more than that.

00:17:44.995 --> 00:17:48.035
His whole energy
has changed, too.

00:17:48.068 --> 00:17:49.437
Where's everyone else?

00:17:49.471 --> 00:17:52.009
Majin Buu ate them.
They're all dead!

00:17:52.043 --> 00:17:54.849
What? You mean Mom
and Dende--everyone?

00:17:54.883 --> 00:17:56.151
Yeah, that's right.

00:17:56.184 --> 00:17:58.322
He took 'em and now
we're the only ones left!

00:17:58.355 --> 00:18:01.361
[GOHAN] No, not Dende, too!
That can't be!

00:18:01.395 --> 00:18:03.432
If he's dead, then the
Dragon Balls are gone, too,

00:18:03.465 --> 00:18:04.903
and our whole plan is ruined!

00:18:04.936 --> 00:18:06.540
We can't bring anyone back!

00:18:06.573 --> 00:18:09.511
[SUPER BUU laughs]
They were very tasty.

00:18:09.545 --> 00:18:13.787
I turned them all to chocolate.
A satisfying snack.

00:18:13.820 --> 00:18:15.790
[grunts]

00:18:17.193 --> 00:18:19.031
[GOHAN]
No, he's wrong.

00:18:19.064 --> 00:18:22.203
The energy's faint,
but I can sense it.

00:18:22.236 --> 00:18:23.640
[GOHAN chuckles]

00:18:23.674 --> 00:18:25.409
Aah!

00:18:29.718 --> 00:18:39.738
♪

00:18:48.489 --> 00:18:50.493
Okay, son! It's time
to show that bully

00:18:50.527 --> 00:18:52.363
the true depths
of your new power!

00:18:52.396 --> 00:18:53.700
I have to admit, Supreme Kai,

00:18:53.733 --> 00:18:55.436
when you told me
you were planning to bring

00:18:55.470 --> 00:18:58.610
a lowly mortal to this hallowed
sanctuary, it didn't make sense.

00:18:58.643 --> 00:19:00.412
He didn't have
any business stepping foot

00:19:00.446 --> 00:19:01.983
on the World of the Kais.

00:19:02.016 --> 00:19:03.586
Yes, I know.
But now you can see

00:19:03.620 --> 00:19:05.557
that my intuition
was right from the start.

00:19:05.591 --> 00:19:08.863
Yes. And you've proven the
legend of the Z Sword was true,

00:19:08.896 --> 00:19:10.433
even if we didn't understand it,

00:19:10.466 --> 00:19:12.403
because the power
it bestowed didn't come from

00:19:12.436 --> 00:19:15.142
the Sword itself,
but from this Grand Supreme Kai

00:19:15.176 --> 00:19:16.546
who was sealed within it.

00:19:16.579 --> 00:19:18.683
Trust me, you weren't
the only one who was surprised.

00:19:18.717 --> 00:19:21.388
I can't believe in 14
generations of Supreme Kai,

00:19:21.422 --> 00:19:23.560
not one was strong enough
to break the seal.

00:19:23.593 --> 00:19:26.298
I guess they don't make 'em
like they used to.

00:19:26.332 --> 00:19:28.503
[SUPREME KAI] I'm sorry
for our shortcomings.

00:19:28.536 --> 00:19:30.239
But even though
it's not what you expected,

00:19:30.273 --> 00:19:32.443
I hope you'll agree
it's working out for the best.

00:19:32.476 --> 00:19:33.847
After all,
the human planet should be

00:19:33.880 --> 00:19:36.586
protected by humans
themselves, don't you agree?

00:19:36.619 --> 00:19:39.390
Yeah, I think so, too.
You can't give us our future,

00:19:39.424 --> 00:19:41.428
we've got to
fight for it ourselves.

00:19:41.461 --> 00:19:43.198
Or we won't treasure
the world we've got.

00:19:43.232 --> 00:19:44.467
We'll take it for granted.

00:19:44.500 --> 00:19:45.970
Struggling, really earning it--

00:19:46.004 --> 00:19:49.177
that's the only way
we'll appreciate being alive.

00:19:49.210 --> 00:19:52.450
Uh! Oh yeah, but I'm not
alive anymore, am I?

00:19:52.483 --> 00:19:54.955
So I guess I'm not
making too much sense, huh?

00:19:54.989 --> 00:19:56.358
[laughing]

00:19:56.391 --> 00:19:59.799
Hm. But you're absolutely
right, Goku; alive or not.

00:19:59.832 --> 00:20:00.801
[ELDER KAI grunts]

00:20:00.834 --> 00:20:02.671
I didn't wait all those
eons in that sword

00:20:02.704 --> 00:20:06.044
just to hear you pups prattle on
with your so-called wisdom!

00:20:06.078 --> 00:20:08.983
I'm the elder,
that's <i>my</i> job! Hmph!

00:20:10.253 --> 00:20:11.756
Just a little respect!

00:20:11.789 --> 00:20:14.327
Next you'll be reading
my magazines, too!

00:20:14.361 --> 00:20:17.467
[SUPREME KAI] But we do
respect you, of course!

00:20:17.500 --> 00:20:19.739
[GOKU] Good luck, Gohan.
You can do it.

00:20:19.772 --> 00:20:22.945
The fate of the earth
depends on you.

00:20:22.979 --> 00:20:24.748
[SUPER BUU chuckles]

00:20:24.782 --> 00:20:29.692
Boy. Come on. Are you
really planning to fight me?

00:20:29.725 --> 00:20:34.034
Fight you? No,
I'm planning to kill you.

00:20:34.067 --> 00:20:38.341
Err!
[laughing]

00:20:38.375 --> 00:20:42.316
I remember you now!
I knocked you out in the desert!

00:20:42.349 --> 00:20:43.853
[PICCOLO]
It's not going to work.

00:20:43.887 --> 00:20:47.293
It's clear Gohan's reached a new
level, but it won't be enough.

00:20:47.326 --> 00:20:49.832
He can't defeat Majin Buu
in a straight fight.

00:20:49.865 --> 00:20:52.403
He needs our help!
We've got to do Fusion again,

00:20:52.436 --> 00:20:54.374
so we can all fight together!

00:20:54.407 --> 00:20:56.378
We can't!
It takes time to recover.

00:20:56.411 --> 00:20:57.581
You know how it works!

00:20:57.614 --> 00:20:59.417
That's what my dad
told us. I know.

00:20:59.450 --> 00:21:01.923
But I don't care--let's try it!

00:21:01.956 --> 00:21:04.962
I can't just stand here and
watch him hurt my brother!

00:21:04.995 --> 00:21:06.599
Okay.

00:21:07.701 --> 00:21:10.405
Yeah. Possible or not,
it can't hurt to try!

00:21:10.439 --> 00:21:12.309
[GOTEN]
Right!

00:21:13.880 --> 00:21:16.686
[PICCOLO]
Huh?

00:21:16.719 --> 00:21:17.888
[BOTH]
Now!

00:21:17.921 --> 00:21:20.893
[NARRATOR] Gohan has received
the ultimate power up

00:21:20.927 --> 00:21:25.804
from an ancient Kai, and has
returned to face Majin Buu.

00:21:25.837 --> 00:21:30.112
As a boy, he was the answer
to saving the world from Cell.

00:21:30.146 --> 00:21:35.490
Now, he will try to rescue the
earth from an even darker day.

00:21:35.524 --> 00:21:38.529
Next Dragon Ball Z Kai!

00:21:40.399 --> 00:21:45.577
♪ Closing Song ♪

00:22:45.462 --> 00:22:46.865
[GOKU]
Hey! It's me, Goku!

00:22:46.899 --> 00:22:49.838
I can't wait to see Gohan's
new powers in action!

00:22:49.872 --> 00:22:53.613
[PICCOLO] Astonishing! How can
he be stronger than Majin Buu?

00:22:53.646 --> 00:22:55.783
He hasn't even
gone Super Saiyan!

00:22:55.817 --> 00:22:59.391
[SUPER BUU] No one is stronger
than me! I won't allow it!

00:22:59.424 --> 00:23:01.629
[GOKU]
Next time, on Dragon Ball Z Kai!

00:23:06.004 --> 00:23:07.306
[GOHAN]
What's wrong, Buu?

00:23:07.339 --> 00:23:09.443
I thought you were
gonna kick my ass!

